{"tid":84196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合醫院男童疑遭侵犯 高永文指事件嚴重","createTime":"2017-01-17T11:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T17:13:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77de77b72c013f51f0a3eb7e51e10f3483166a35","tid":84196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>聯合醫院一13歲男童疑遭侵犯　高永文指事件嚴重</strong><br />\n2017-01-17 HKT 15:59<br />\n<br />\n繼九龍醫院發生病人遭性侵事件後，聯合醫院被指有一名13歲男童，在上月留醫<strong>精神科病房</strong>期間疑遭到侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長高永文指事件嚴重，<span style=\"color: red;\">事件不只在一間醫院發生</span>，因此今日已與醫管局溝通，醫管局總辦事處將會緊急開會，與所有精神科單位討論事件。<br />\n<br />\n高永文說，相信連同較早前的事件，希望醫管局能整體檢視所有精神科醫院及病房的設施、程序、指引及人手，能<strong>如何保護沒有能力保護自己的病人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於個案的詳情，高永文說相信要交由警方調查，強調醫管局會認真跟進。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1308126-20170117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1308126-20170117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYuQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=4d3c2de2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1308126-20170117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4fa4871f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1308126-20170117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2cdc93b01a6017c129fbe83853fdf06faae7da23","tid":84196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899904753e9fd78eb2a69f31b8d33f62e2ebb62a","tid":84196,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"東區醫院都有一單性侵弱智兒童<br />\n不過吿唔入"},{"pid":"3e808e7e235f275e8675f6884a44170b0c0c2387","tid":84196,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"好難想像係香港發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" 